00:21.569 --> 00:23.038
See how the deer
changed direction

00:23.106 --> 00:25.076
when he heard us coming.

00:27.446 --> 00:29.748
Can you tell me
which way he went?

00:29.815 --> 00:32.348
I don't see why
I need to learn to hunt.

00:32.415 --> 00:33.950
We're not in
a Mord-Sith temple.

00:34.017 --> 00:35.550
We don't have
slaves to bring us dinner.

00:35.618 --> 00:38.118
I'm here to protect you,
Richard,

00:38.186 --> 00:40.052
not provide meals.

00:42.423 --> 00:44.192
Kahlan's not above
digging up roots.

00:44.261 --> 00:48.229
Even Zedd's been known to do
the washing now and then.

00:48.295 --> 00:50.026
We all need to contribute.

00:57.090 --> 01:00.024
Are you saying I'm not
doing enough for you?

01:03.292 --> 01:05.426
Just tell me which way
the deer went.

01:09.095 --> 01:10.695
That way.

01:10.763 --> 01:12.130
Where the bark has rubbed
off the tree.

01:14.165 --> 01:16.065
See, I knew you'd be
good at this.

01:18.000 --> 01:24.074
Advertise your product or brand here
